    lia "没错。Ophelia·Starhead所著的多卷编年史。“Starhead王朝三人列传”。[mename]，[孩子名]，还有……贝里克。"

# game/a12/6wife_brith.rpy:1438
translate english wife_brith3_aur_26ab40b2:

